<D>__{shall we invite your wife in now?}
<A>__{logue goes to the door and starts to open it. he shuts it quickly.}
<C>__{lionel }
<D>__{i wasn't expecting myrtle for several hours!}
<A>__{in the parlour: myrtle has entered, definitely unhappy. seeing elizabeth, she's even less happy, and flabbergasted.}
